title: Deadly Weapons - La Chiamavano Susy Tettalunga - 1974
description:
TITLE: Deadly Weapons
AKA: La Chiamavano Susy Tettalunga
YEAR: 1974

Crystal is an advertising executive who tracks down the mobsters who killed her boyfriend Larry. One by one, she seduces each man, drugs them, then smothers them to death with her large breasts. At the end, she finds out that it was her own father (Phillip Stahl) who ordered her lover's execution.
